# Photo sources for the Appraiser rehab vision pipeline (Phase 4B.1).
# Both required for collectPhotos() in lib/photo-sources.ts. When either
# is missing the rehab GET endpoint returns no_photos_available (422)
# and the operator unlocks the INV-005 manual fallback affordance in
# AppraiserRehabPanel. The nightly retry cron re-attempts vision once
# the keys are restored and surfaces drift via Notes marker.
SCRAPER_API_KEY=your_scraperapi_key
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key
